  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/pull/346",
  "title": "chore(shrinkwrap): use uber/shrinkwrap",
  "body": "PROS:\n- consistent shrinkwrap, removes \"from\" weird things\n- we should now be able to have a lot less noise when updating/adding\n  modules\n\nCONS:\n- need to be installed globally (weird stuff happens otherwise)\n- not compatible with npm@3\n\nThis is currently my best solution to the shrinkwrap madness.\n\nI updated the contributing guide, a lot easier now and faster to add,\nupdate, remove packages.\n\nI hope npm@3 gets better at shrinkwrap some day.\n\nAlso:\n- removed a bunch of packages we did not use anymore\n- updated some packages\n- updated our linting rules with more defaults for react\n",
